as read on television:
   Defense and Interior _ Maj. Gen. Williams Regala, who was a
member of Namphy's three-member junta.
   Foreign Relations _ Brig. Gen. Herard Abraham, who had the same
portfolio under the junta.
   Information _ Col. Alsidius Saint Louis.
   Economy and Finance _ Col. Andre Jean-Pierre.
   Justice _ Brig. Gen. Fritz Antoine.
   Public Health and Population _ Lt. Col. Jean Verly.
