Desulme.
   Agriculture _ Lt. Col. Donmax Citasus (phonetic spelling).
   Education, Youth and Sports _ Brig. Gen. Cecilio Dorce.
   Social Affairs _ Col. Fred Desyr, minister of Social Affairs.
   Commerce and Industry _ Col. Eric Brunel Lamour (phonetic
spelling).
   National Promotions and Public Administration _ Claude Grand
Pierre, apparently the only civilian.
