<HEAD>Soviet Cosmonauts Honor American Astronaut</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WEATHERFORD, Okla. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Astronaut Thomas Stafford linked up
again with a Soviet cosmonaut 13 years after they flew together in
space in the Apollo-Soyuz mission, but this time they were in a
downtown park in his hometown.
