<1ST_LINE>u p AM-Dukakis 1stLd-Writethru a0757 06-21 0570</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Dukakis, 1st Ld-Writethru, a0757,590</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>Eds: Top 14 grafs new to UPDATE with Dukakis and Jackson remarks;
